#1. 웹 브라우저에 뉴스 페이지를 3개 불러오고, 다운로드 받으시오
library(rvest)
## Loading required package: xml2
url1 <-"https://news.v.daum.net/v/20180801060105364"
url2 <- "https://news.v.daum.net/v/20180801000519618?d=y"
url3 <- "https://news.v.daum.net/v/20180801030831465"

ht1 <- read_html(url1)
ht2 <- read_html(url2)
ht3 <- read_html(url3)

contents1 <- html_node(ht1,"#harmonyContainer") %>% html_text()
contents2 <- html_node(ht2, "#harmonyContainer") %>% html_text()
contents3 <- html_node(ht3, "#harmonyContainer") %>% html_text()

contents1 <- stringr::str_replace_all(contents1,"\r"," " )
contents1 <- stringr::str_replace_all(contents1,"\n"," " )
contents1 <- stringr::str_replace_all(contents1,"[:punct:]"," " )
contents1 <- stringr::str_replace_all(contents1,"[a-zA-Z]"," " )

contents2 <- stringr::str_replace_all(contents2,"\r"," " )
contents2 <- stringr::str_replace_all(contents2,"\n"," " )
contents2 <- stringr::str_replace_all(contents2,"[:punct:]"," " )
contents2 <- stringr::str_replace_all(contents2,"[a-zA-Z]"," " )

contents3 <- stringr::str_replace_all(contents3,"\r"," " )
contents3 <- stringr::str_replace_all(contents3,"\n"," " )
contents3 <- stringr::str_replace_all(contents3,"[:punct:]"," " )
contents3 <- stringr::str_replace_all(contents3,"[a-zA-Z]"," " )


write.csv(contents1, "contents1.csv")
write.csv(contents2, "contents2.csv")
write.csv(contents3, "contents3.csv")

1.5 고빈도 단어 추출

txt <- readLines("sample_news.txt")
noun <- lapply(txt, getMorph, "noun")
nounVec <- unlist(noun)
nounFreq <- table(nounVec)
word <- nounFreq %>% sort( decreasing = T) %>% head(20) %>% names()
freq <- nounFreq %>% sort( decreasing = T) %>% head(20) %>% as.vector()

sum <- sum(nounFreq)
percent <- round(freq/sum*100, digits = 2)

mainTxt <- "고빈도 단어"
bp <- barplot(percent, main=mainTxt, las=2, ylim=c(0,5), ylab = "%", names.arg = word, col="black")
# x축 설명의 이름 방향( las ): 가로=1 세로=2
# ylim 으로 y축의 총 폭을 결정함.

text(x=bp, y=percent + 0.1, labels=paste(freq), col="black", cex=0.8)


2. 키워드 분석

2.1 워드 클라우드

txt <- readLines("sample_news.txt")
noun <- lapply(txt, getMorph, "noun")
nounVec <- unlist(noun)
nounFreq <- table(nounVec)

#install.packages("RColorBrewer"); 
library(RColorBrewer)
#install.packages("wordcloud")
library(wordcloud)

pal <- brewer.pal(8, "Dark2")
wordcloud(names(nounFreq), freq=nounFreq, scale=c(4,1), rot.per=0.25, min.freq=30, random.order = F, random.color = T, colors=pal)

# names : 목록 얻기
# freq : 그 목록의 빈도
# scale=c(글자최대크기, 글자최소크기)
# rot.per : 90도로 눕혀진 글자들의 비율
# min.freq = 최소 빈도 기준
# random.orde : 글자를 랜덤으로 놓을지 여부, 'F'이면 내림차순으로 정렬
# random.color : 색상을 랜덤으로 놓을지 여부, 'F'이면 색상이 빈도에 따라 선택됨
# colors : 색상 팔레트("blue", "black" 등도됨)

require(stringr)
## Loading required package: stringr
text <- tweets.text
x <- gsub("[^A-Za-z가-힣[:space:][:digit:][:punct:]]", "", text)
x <- gsub("@|\n|RT", "", x)
x <- gsub("[[:punct:]]", " ", x)
x <- gsub("[[:digit:]]", "", x)
x <- tolower(x)
x <- gsub("[a-z]", "", x)
x <- str_trim(x)

## [50] "잘났다 정말 대한민국 민주주의 포기해 다섯명의 황제들에게 맡겨"
#library(RHINO)
x1 <- lapply(x, getMorph)
x2 <- lapply(x1, function(x) x[nchar(x)>1])
x3 <- do.call(c, x2)
o <- table(x3)

#install.packages("wordcloud")
#library(wordcloud)
pal <- brewer.pal(8,"Dark2")
wordcloud(names(o), o, min.freq=3, random.order=F,random.color=T,colors=pal)

###########################막대그래프################################
word <- o %>% sort( decreasing = T) %>% head(20) %>% names()
freq <- o %>% sort( decreasing = T) %>% head(20) %>% as.vector()

sum <- sum(nounFreq)
percent <- round(freq/sum*100, digits = 2)

mainTxt <- "고빈도 단어"
bp <- barplot(percent, main=mainTxt, las=2, ylim=c(0,300), ylab = "%", names.arg = word, col="black")
# x축 설명의 이름 방향( las ): 가로=1 세로=2
# ylim 으로 y축의 총 폭을 결정함.

text(x=bp, y=percent + 15, labels=paste(freq), col="black", cex=0.8)
